			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I was wondering how these work, on Lucy it says they migate 100/5/100 for Guard II and 100/5/200 for guard III.  Anyone know what those numbers represent?  And has anyone done this and can tell me if your happy with your decision?
<br />

<br />
I use my epic in my offhand, if it matters.
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance</span></td>
