				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi,
<br />
  I had guard 2 on one of my weapons.  It proc'd often.  It's effect seemed to reduce incoming melee damage by 5% per hit until its max was reached (max being 50- 100 total damage absorbed).
<br />

<br />
It saves you on hp over time by reducing the damage you would normally have taken.  I believe lifetaps would work better.  I sold my guard2 aug back and am saving for the 75hp lifetap.
<br />

<br />
-ruser-</span></td>
