				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Thinking about putting Guard II or Guard III on my epic...<a name="60977"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 8 04 10:16 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>For anything except melee soloing (a la melee-mezz soloing, where life tap proc augs are definitely the BIG win), it's my own opinion that it's the raw damage DD-type procs that are the win.  Specifically, the RUJ 125 point DD poison based proc aug and the MIR 150 DD cold based proc aug.
<br />

<br />
If you are in xp groups a lot (versus melee soloing), the lifetap procs aren't as efficient.  I've found that regen coupled with player heals simply don't make the lifetaps worth their cost.
